graph LR
    CodeFlare[CodeFlare Operator<br/>RHOAI Component]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    CodeFlare -->|requires CRD| KubeRay[KubeRay Operator<br/>v1.1.0+<br/>RayCluster CRD]
    CodeFlare -->|workload queueing| Kueue[Kueue<br/>v0.7.0+<br/>Resource quotas]
    CodeFlare -->|cert rotation| CertController[cert-controller<br/>v0.10.1+<br/>Webhook TLS certs]
    CodeFlare -->|orchestration| K8s[Kubernetes<br/>1.29+<br/>API Server]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional - OpenShift)
    CodeFlare -.->|OAuth proxy| OpenShift[OpenShift 4.x<br/>Optional<br/>OAuth + Routes + service-ca]

    %% External Libraries
    CodeFlare -->|gang scheduling| AppWrapperLib[AppWrapper Library<br/>v0.20.2+<br/>Embedded controller]

    %% Internal ODH/RHOAI Dependencies
    CodeFlare -->|platform config| ODHOperator[ODH Operator<br/>DSCInitialization CRD]
    CodeFlare -.->|optional monitoring| ServiceMesh[Service Mesh<br/>mTLS sidecars]

    %% Integration Points (consumers)
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>UI management] -->|monitors| CodeFlare
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines<br/>MLOps workflows] -->|auto-deploy| CodeFlare
    SDK[CodeFlare SDK<br/>Python client library] -->|creates resources| CodeFlare

    %% Monitoring
    CodeFlare -->|exposes metrics| Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>Metrics collection]

    %% Managed Resources
    CodeFlare -->|creates/manages| RayCluster[Ray Cluster<br/>Distributed compute<br/>with OAuth + mTLS]
    CodeFlare -->|creates/manages| AppWrapper[AppWrapper<br/>Gang scheduling<br/>Kueue integration]

    %% Ray Cluster Dependencies
    RayCluster -.->|uses| KubeRay
    RayCluster -.->|secured by| OpenShift
    AppWrapper -.->|queued by| Kueue

    %% Styling
    style CodeFlare fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff

